where Kn is the Knudsen number defined as Kn = λ/h, λ is the mean free path of molecules and h the gap distance. Based on different derivation considerations, one can get different viscosity definitions, as in Hsia and Domoto (1983). The mean free path of air molecules at ambient pressure Pa is about 65 nm.

